{"tid":1809814,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"光復後充公及拍賣中聯辦、官員及警察財產來賠償香港嘅損失嘅可行性","createTime":"2020-01-03T11:00:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T11:54:47.000Z","uid":312125,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5f99f0e5cddb2847b4660b9d95952c16f23a26f3","tid":1809814,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T11:00:58.000Z","msg":"香港光復之後，應該要對因暴政而造成嘅人命、財產損失作出估算，並將全部官員及警察收監，凍結及充公佢地全家資產，然後拍賣來抵償因暴政帶來人命傷亡、設施及店鋪破壞等。如果都唔夠賠，要捉埋佢仔女坐監，如果篤灰嘅可以免刑<br />\n<br />\n諗起都開心，請大家探討以上建議嘅可行性<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1488d5e5e3a11077b351ba90389446016d4eca4","tid":1809814,"uid":62020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T11:04:46.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"5a00b2720f3a462928c539952a0ca8d88627b91a","tid":1809814,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T11:05:18.000Z","msg":"拆咗中聯辦棟樓走唔甩<br />\n風水陣嚟"},{"pid":"e8db392f6d3722099806e6a22791f73834386bc5","tid":1809814,"uid":27250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T11:07:17.000Z","msg":"學台灣整條滲透法，充公晒支共、支企、藍絲、愛港愛國副身家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f82bd94fb830af68d0bb7ae385575a8be626917e","tid":1809814,"uid":121562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T11:54:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}